# Query Documents

  Ugh: lots of confusing syntactic sugar!

** https://docs.mongodb.com/v4.0/core/databases-and-collections/

Starting in MongoDB 3.2, however, you can enforce document validation rules for
a collection during update and insert operations. See Schema Validation for
details.
